I like to use boon on my main tank.  As soon as he procs a lifetap on the target, it is safe to tash.  After the second proc it is usually safe to med/sit.  You can treat things like yak procs or critical hits as agro magnets.  Rangers are the best with snare and taunt.<P>My 2 CP.<BR>-Juju-
