I think the difference in "reaction" to tash is simply the differences in how various mobs aggro.<P>When the aggro on tash was capped, Verant then stated that the aggro from debuffs is proportional to the HP of the mob, so mobs with huge HP totals were generating too much aggro.<P>Arlina
