Times I use tash:<P>Places with higher than normal resists; doing slows in Seb (slightly higher than normal) or doing anything on Cleric Molkars and Seahorsies in Siren's Grotto.<P>When lowering resists is more important than usual; I tash when I plan to chain stun a mob, or when I have spare time between AE mez refreshes and I'm not being lazy.<P>Other casters having trouble; a lower level shaman might have trouble sticking a slow without tash, and it improves efficiency on magic based nukes such as the ultra efficient ultra resistable Tears of Druzzil.<P>Arlina
